            {
                "h2": "ðŸ”— AJAX & Pipe Elements"
            },
            {
                "p": {"textcontent": "The <pipe> element is the workhorse of dotPipe for loading remote content. It makes AJAX requests declaratively without writing JavaScript."}
            },

            {
                "h3": "ðŸ“¡ Basic AJAX Loading"
